Class RoomChangeEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node
      • javafx.scene.shape.Shape
        • javafx.scene.shape.Rectangle
          • utilities.Entity
            • components.RoomChangeEntity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget

    public class RoomChangeEntity
extends Entity
    Entity that, when the player intersects with it, can interact with it and/or change rooms. The action upon the interaction is given through a ChangeRequest.
    Since:
    4.0, 6/6/2022
